<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:14:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国设立475亿美元国家基金促进半导体产业发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-sets-up-475-bln-state-fund-boost-semiconductor-industry-2024-05-27/</link><description>中国设立了一个新的国家支持投资基金，注册资本为 3440 亿元人民币（475 亿美元），以促进该国的半导体产业发展。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:11:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-sets-up-475-bln-state-fund-boost-semiconductor-industry-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国“资产荒”抑制央行债券交易雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/asset-famine-china-curbs-central-banks-bond-trading-ambitions-2024-05-27/</link><description>中国金融部门低风险资产的稀缺正在阻碍央行在中断17年后重返国债市场以提高其货币政策工具箱效率的计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:55:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/asset-famine-china-curbs-central-banks-bond-trading-ambitions-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>发言人称日本要求朝鲜取消卫星火箭发射</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-demands-north-korea-cancel-satellite-rocket-launch-spokesperson-says-2024-05-27/</link><description>日本政府最高发言人、内阁官房长官林芳正周一表示，东京已通过北京的外交渠道要求朝鲜取消计划的卫星火箭发射。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-demands-north-korea-cancel-satellite-rocket-launch-spokesperson-says-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产开发商佳兆业清算听证会延期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-court-adjourns-liquidation-hearing-china-developer-kaisa-2024-05-27/</link><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求佳兆业集团清算的请愿书的听证会推迟至 6 月 24 日，这让这家陷入困境的中国开发商在实施债务重组计划时得到了一些喘息的机会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-court-adjourns-liquidation-hearing-china-developer-kaisa-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>1-4月全国规模以上工业利润增长4.3%，与一季度持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-profits-rise-43-jan-april-unchanged-q1-2024-05-27/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，今年前四个月中国工业企业利润同比增长4.3%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 01:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-profits-rise-43-jan-april-unchanged-q1-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>全球通胀数据公布前美元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-global-inflation-data-2024-05-27/</link><description>美元本周开局稳定，投资者关注美国、欧洲和日本通胀数据以指导全球利率前景。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 01:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-global-inflation-data-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国和欧盟通胀数据的临近，亚洲股​​市攀升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-27/</link><description>亚洲股市周一小幅走高，因投资者准备迎接繁忙的一周数据，最终将公布美国关键通胀报告，该报告可能为降息奠定基础，尽管还需要几个月的时间。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 00:25:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理欢呼与美国盟友韩国、日本的“新开始”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-premier-hold-rare-summit-with-us-allied-south-korea-japan-2024-05-26/</link><description>四年来的首次三方会谈旨在恢复因全球紧张局势而受阻的贸易和安全对话。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 22:33:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-premier-hold-rare-summit-with-us-allied-south-korea-japan-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>官员称巴基斯坦逮捕了11名参与杀害中国工程师的武装分子</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-arrests-11-militants-involved-chinese-engineers-killing-say-officials-2024-05-26/</link><description>官员周日表示，巴基斯坦当局逮捕了 11 名伊斯兰激进分子，他们参与了 3 月份在该国北部与阿富汗接壤的自杀式爆炸事件，导致 5 名中国工程师死亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-arrests-11-militants-involved-chinese-engineers-killing-say-officials-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员本周访问台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-visiting-taiwan-this-week-2024-05-26/</link><description>事实上的美国大使馆周日表示，由众议院外交事务委员会主席迈克尔·麦考尔率领的美国议员代表团本周将访问台湾。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 11:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-visiting-taiwan-this-week-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>李强总理表示鼓励三星加大对华投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/samsung-encouraged-invest-more-china-premier-li-qiang-says-2024-05-26/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，中国总理李强周日对三星董事长李在镕表示，中国欢迎这家韩国企业集团进一步投资，因为中国市场的外国企业正在努力应对地缘政治的不确定性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 11:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/samsung-encouraged-invest-more-china-premier-li-qiang-says-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>与中国前线的台湾酒吧将历史融入鸡尾酒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-bar-frontline-with-china-blends-history-into-cocktails-2024-05-26/</link><description>在距离中国厦门和泉州不到一小时船程的台湾金门，酒吧老板 Powei Lee 将这个小岛的战争恐惧的过去融入鸡尾酒中，吸引了大批人群。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 04:26:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-bar-frontline-with-china-blends-history-into-cocktails-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国与美国盟友韩国、日本讨论安全和商业问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-li-lands-seoul-trilateral-summit-with-south-korea-japan-2024-05-26/</link><description>中国国务院总理李强周日与韩国总统尹锡烈同意启动外交安全对话并恢复自由贸易谈判，并与日本首相岸田文雄讨论了台湾地区的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-li-lands-seoul-trilateral-summit-with-south-korea-japan-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国演习后台湾总统表达善意，美国议员抵达</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/after-china-drills-taiwan-president-again-offers-talks-2024-05-26/</link><description>中国多次痛斥赖清德为“分裂分子”，并拒绝了他的会谈提议。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:10:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/after-china-drills-taiwan-president-again-offers-talks-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾日益政治化的变装皇后在主场令粉丝惊叹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-increasingly-political-drag-race-queen-wows-fans-home-stage-2024-05-26/</link><description>台湾选手 Nymphia Wind 是第一个在鲁保罗变装皇后秀中夺得桂冠的东亚人，也是一个日益政治化的人物，她在台北举行的大型返校演出中让数百名粉丝惊叹不已。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 01:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-increasingly-political-drag-race-queen-wows-fans-home-stage-2024-05-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>